# The API. The market WebSocket (real Binance prices) is served from here.
#
# The frontend never computes a price — it renders what this sends (AGENTS.md §6).
# With the API down, prices read "Waiting for price…" rather than showing an
# invented number, which is the whole reason the live-price mock was deleted.
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
